        \item Is there an individual right to water?
        \item Do nation states have a right to water?
        \item Does it matter if you're oil-rich Saudi Arabia or the (relatively) poor
        and low-lying Republic of the Marshall Islands?
        \item Discuss how these rights impact global efforts to limit climate change.
        \end{enumerate}

  \item Consider a carbon tax on commercial transportation.
